{"tid":1588721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15歲少女淚揭男友「5個月要4次」：愛我就要給我","createTime":"2019-09-23T02:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T03:25:20.000Z","uid":31254,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"aee921ce534faeff4948cff758389156157e4a6a","tid":1588721,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:58:36.000Z","msg":"桃園15歲少女淚揭男友「5個月要4次」：愛我就要給我<br />\n<br />\n記者張靖榕／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n桃園20歲廖姓男子在5個月內，4度和15歲的小女友天晴（化名）發生性行為。天晴和她母親事後控告廖男性侵，稱被廖男威脅「愛我就要給我」；廖男則表示上床時天晴雖「半推半就」，但從沒有強迫對方。高等法院認定廖並未涉強制性交罪等重罪，不過確實有4個「與少女性交罪」，最後判處廖男6月徒刑，沒有緩刑也不得易科罰金。全案可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n一審判決書指出，當時18歲的廖男從2017年7月下旬開始，首次和當時只有15歲的女朋友天晴發生性關係，地點分別是廖男桃園住家和天晴住處等地方，到了12月時，和對方性交次數共4次。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n天晴的母親得知此事，氣得告上桃園地院，指控廖男違反天晴意願；天晴指出，廖男雖然沒有動手毆打或強迫的行為，但上床前會說「愛我就要給我啊」等語。對此，廖男在庭上坦承和天晴4度發生性關係，第一次對方雖然半推半就，自己也有硬脫褲子的舉動，但沒有強迫或威脅對方。<br />\n<br />\n廖男當庭提出20萬元想和天晴和解，但被天晴和母親拒絕。《自由時報》報導，高等法院判斷雖然第一次是半推半就情況，但當下天晴仍有自主權，而且若是違反意願，之後也不會繼續和對方發生關係；然而天晴及母親不願原諒廖男，法官審酌後判廖男6月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b82bf6f183e6311656f52a335ec13e8c31d2887","tid":1588721,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"1524824e800dc2ad954c6a019c2c6c7dcf6e73b3","tid":1588721,"uid":38352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:59:12.000Z","msg":"桃園 1分"},{"pid":"45b7abfa2ab59f0ad1e2cf1affbcadc0889f39ad","tid":1588721,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"不推文"},{"pid":"e10ef121074d971fecd3bb003364f7f28ecf99c4","tid":1588721,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"5個月先4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2765f1e9a084d7c8a89239cf4783139e3cc10c69","tid":1588721,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"愛我請留言"},{"pid":"8211e1505ad0e08be2fa866239f1729265237c34","tid":1588721,"uid":69168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"5個月4次都算忍得"},{"pid":"4efaf9a0f782e10d0070c657282c9d774cdbc503","tid":1588721,"uid":311193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e10ef121074d971fecd3bb003364f7f28ecf99c4","tid":1588721,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"5個月先4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"我都咁諗 咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff634619a30bd1420b4a0c1fc987e909fb215c0","tid":1588721,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e10ef121074d971fecd3bb003364f7f28ecf99c4","tid":1588721,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"5個月先4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"只加一分"},{"pid":"e331d1195552c0a12cca1e93513ef4877832cfb2","tid":1588721,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"有咩好報導<br />\n最多都係同未成年搞野姐<br />\n<br />\n打文條友錯重點<br />\n咪以為網民鐘意睇扑野<br />\n就打「5個月要4次」<br />\n<br />\n定係單案係5個月40次...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e92ee88f382a676fa32a5039a70277b5d796c4b","tid":1588721,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23